  "texts": [
    "These 26 quantitative indicators can be divided into three categories: simple indicators, statistical indicators and information theory indicators.",
    "1 Number of variables (P). 2 Sample size (N).",
    "3 Number of categories (N_class).",
    "4 Ratio of largest class (R_largest).",
    "5 Ratio of least class (R_least)."
  ]
